							<tr width="90%"><td width="60%">상품 / 옵션정보</td><td>수량</td><td>주문금액</td></tr>
						</thead>
						<tbody>
							<tr><td><img src="product/${order.order_img}">&nbsp; 상품명 : ${order.order_product} / 사이즈 : ${order.order_size}</td><td>${order.order_qty}</td><td>${order.order_price}</td></tr>
